cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.ET, cs.PF 

The paper proposes a coordinated optimal scheduling model for hybrid AC/DC microgrids, which involves the integration of power systems, control systems, and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also deals with power flow equations and optimization problems, which are relevant to cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) and cs.PF (Power and Energy).
